{"tid":2061030,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍絲阿叔：我當時有試過上唔知咩網，話黃之鋒有口罩賣啊嘛……不過買唔到","createTime":"2020-06-12T05:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T07:27:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0f8e491b31c27af61da3612e759b387dcbcebb","tid":2061030,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:48:37.000Z","msg":"【關於街站被啊叔罵我勾結外國勢力】<br />\n<br />\n今朝同觀塘願景 - 梁凱晴 Jannelle R. Leung去樂富擺站，雖然勁曬但都反應好好，不過最值得一提既，就係遇到成班長者排隊拎免費大公報，結果不出所料，有位興致勃勃既藍絲啊叔，真係走來關照我：<br />\n<br />\n啊叔：「漢奸！走狗！賣國賊！」<br />\n<br />\n我：「呢位啊叔，雖然今日天氣好熱，但晨早流流又唔使咁燥，不如你講下我邊度賣國啊？」<br />\n<br />\n啊叔：「中國人梗係撐中國，但你成日去外國，搵咩美國佬，根本係勾結外國勢力！」<br />\n<br />\n我：「咪就係因為有外國聯繫，所以三月疫情爆得最勁果時，我先喺美洲同埋各地，加加埋埋買到一百五萬個口罩返香港，咁你話外國勢力有無用啊？」<br />\n<br />\n之後啊叔唔出聲，但又唔行開&hellip;&hellip;為免deadair我就繼續講話：<br />\n<br />\n我：「所以呢&hellip;&hellip;有口罩真係好緊要架，果時我地賣口罩，你有無買啊？」<br />\n<br />\n啊叔：「我當時有試過上唔知咩網，話黃之鋒有口罩賣啊嘛&hellip;&hellip;不過果時買唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「咁咪係囉，話就話中國人撐中國，但要買口罩既時候，你揀美國貨，定係中國貨啊？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，啊叔個樣好無癮咁行開左。<br />\n<br />\n所以話呢，小至街坊街里話愛祖國，但總係想買西方產地既口罩，大至高官諸如楊潤雄話要搞愛國教育，但送曬仔女去國際學校 &mdash;&mdash; 口裡說不，但身體誠實既人，呢個社會真係好多。"},{"pid":"38e486b37bb7c5504d29aed80c9ebce7b79e3ab8","tid":2061030,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"個阿叔又幾撚誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257c0aee45b6296ad0e0507e98b9caf9ed020323","tid":2061030,"uid":200663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"屌你咁快踢爆佢好無面㗎嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ba5b1bbb0877f183205e71d050e086c3afcacb","tid":2061030,"uid":291065,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"佢答呢D on 9問題都答到熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020af9342ff760f48da89eec3c2e42c66108e921","tid":2061030,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"咁能多字<br />\n牙晴啲相呢"},{"pid":"d271ce8d30f7a6c8a6d0f140ae34369d13928284","tid":2061030,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:00:07.000Z","msg":"希望其素人/本土區議員都擺吓街站<br />\n不論民生或政治議題都好<br />\n感覺好多都好少，偏向做咗野然後貼FB<br />\n屌啲師奶唔會知架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06275cdab3b478d189c64afd6d75947ac1636bab","tid":2061030,"uid":225798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:07:40.000Z","msg":"撚狗師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0bf97542cc1623a5fefa850a425b7d6fe6fb1d","tid":2061030,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:13:47.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6cd9aae2c0a16ad1d737cab61ff3d2606145ab","tid":2061030,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"我識既藍絲一樣得把口愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}